-- pd.package: Sitemap Footer
name: fifthtry.github.io/footer

`sitemap-footer` is another footer component which shows sections from your
`fastn` sitemap of `FASTN.ftd`.

Use our `sitemap-footer` on your fast web projects where you would like to show footer on your web pages.

If you are using our `doc-site` as your website theme, then to use `sitemap-footer` add below `fastn` dependency into `FASTN.ftd` file:

-- ft.code:
lang: ftd

\-- fastn.dependency: fifthtry.github.io/doc-site
\-- fastn.dependency: fifthtry.github.io/footer
\-- fastn.auto-import: fifthtry.github.io/doc-site as ds
\-- fastn.auto-import: fifthtry.github.io/footer


-- tf.markdown:

Once you add above lines into your `fastn` package, add `footer` into your `.ftd` 

